name: AUPreset
desc: Used to set factory presets for an audio unit.

items.name: var presetName: Unmanaged<CFString>?
items.desc: If a factory preset, the name of the specified factory preset.

items.name: var presetNumber: Int32
items.desc: If less than 0, then the preset is a user preset. If greater than or equal to 0, then this field is used to select a factory preset.
